08:36.950 --> 08:38.750
Senior Leftenan Ahn diburu.

08:39.970 --> 08:41.640
Mereka memburu dia.

08:41.860 --> 08:43.830
Menurut senjata, pergerakan, keadaan fizikal,

08:44.169 --> 08:46.600
